{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Invaders Tower Defense Online</strong> (ITDO) is an exciting strategy game that combines attack and defense elements. Get ready to build your ultimate defense with a combination of powerful towers and face your opponents with strong invaders. This game offers a unique and immersive experience for all tower defense enthusiasts!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826540/extras/GIFITDO1.gif?t=1734719789\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>1. Balance between Attack and Defense:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Start with 400 credits and 100 lives to defend.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Receive an income of 200 credits per round.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Invaders that cross the board reduce their lives.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Sending raiders costs credits, but also increases your income.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Each round lasts 12 seconds. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>2. Variety of Invaders and Towers:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Fight over 30 different types of attackers. Each attacker has specific abilities and weaknesses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Choose from over 15 types of towers to strategically position. Each tower has its own characteristics and abilities.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>3. Maps and Game Modes:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Explore over 10 different maps, each with unique challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Try different game modes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 1v1 Duel Mode: Take on another player in exciting matches.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 2v2 Team Mode: Form a team with a friend and fight against another duo.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Free-for-All (FFA) mode: All against all! Be the last player standing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Matches against AI: Hone your skills against artificial intelligence.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Defense Mode: Survive as long as you can against waves of increasingly stronger invaders.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"AI Puncher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2826540/118c6d88ec1549836d8e4dc5394ef2fd158e3481.jpg"},{"name":"Bronze Defense","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2826540/d2bfd395f2a7fd6bd2ec513ef54efa2614bf23d9.jpg"},{"name":"Silver Defense","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2826540/232a4bc2aaaab39281e7e88111bd42e3a0f21ebe.jpg"},{"name":"Golden Defense","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2826540/2afed84794a3540c3c3b665929594ca607e921b5.jpg"},{"name":"Diamond Defense","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2826540/b055d9d0ae95547cc63047da00bafe8488dce72f.jpg"},{"name":"This is ITDO","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2826540/bd119aba3ef5d314f4b93f9a21ae1eac6da62961.jpg"},{"name":"Platinum Defense","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2826540/eb121d81664e12bd26f54205badd83873561096c.jpg"},{"name":"Legendary Defense","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2826540/76e39011710caccc672d2aa667e7c50c541f28cc.jpg"}],"total":8},"background":"